### JISHLink API Endpoints
### REST Client / VS Code REST Client compatible
### Usage: Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
###
### Variables — set these before testing:

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = <paste-supabase-admin-jwt-here>
@recruiterToken = <paste-supabase-recruiter-jwt-here>
@employeeToken = <paste-employee-jwt-from-login-response>
@siteId = 30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@employeeId = 40000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###
### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### GET /healthz — server + Supabase connectivity check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

###
### ─── EMPLOYEE AUTH ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### POST /auth/employee/login — authenticate with employee code + password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/employee/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "JL1001",
  "password": "MyPassword123"
}

###

### POST /auth/employee/send-otp — request SMS OTP for login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/employee/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "JL1001",
  "purpose": "login"
}

###

### POST /auth/employee/verify-otp — verify SMS OTP and get JWT
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/employee/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "JL1001",
  "otp": "123456",
  "purpose": "login"
}

###

### POST /auth/employee/forgot-password — send password reset SMS OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/employee/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "JL1001"
}

###

### POST /auth/employee/reset-password — reset password with SMS code
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/employee/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "JL1001",
  "reset_code": "123456",
  "new_password": "NewPassword456"
}

###
### ─── ATTENDANCE SCAN (Employee Bearer token) ─────────────────────────────────
###

### POST /attendance/scan — full QR scan pipeline (check-in)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/scan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "site_token": "qr_mum_central_001",
  "latitude": 18.9748,
  "longitude": 72.8241,
  "device_id": "device_abc_123",
  "timestamp": "2026-07-02T08:05:00.000Z"
}

###

### POST /attendance/scan — check-out (same endpoint, server detects state)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/scan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "site_token": "qr_mum_central_001",
  "latitude": 18.9748,
  "longitude": 72.8241,
  "device_id": "device_abc_123",
  "timestamp": "2026-07-02T17:10:00.000Z"
}

###

### POST /attendance/scan — geofence fail test (far away)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/scan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "site_token": "qr_mum_central_001",
  "latitude": 19.1000,
  "longitude": 72.9000,
  "device_id": "device_abc_123"
}

###
### ─── QR CODE GENERATION (Admin Supabase token) ───────────────────────────────
###

### POST /qr/generate/:siteId — generate/rotate QR code for a site
POST {{baseUrl}}/qr/generate/{{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### ─── DASHBOARD (Admin/Recruiter Supabase token) ──────────────────────────────
###

### GET /dashboard/stats — KPI summary for today
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /dashboard/attendance-trend — 14-day daily attendance trend
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/attendance-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /dashboard/attendance-trend — filtered by site
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/attendance-trend?siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /dashboard/recent-checkins — latest 20 check-ins
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent-checkins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /dashboard/recent-checkins — limit to 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent-checkins?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### ─── REPORTS (Admin/Recruiter Supabase token) ────────────────────────────────
###

### GET /reports/daily — attendance for a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/daily — filtered by site
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?date=2026-07-02&siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/daily — filtered by employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?date=2026-07-02&employeeId={{employeeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/monthly — monthly summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthly?year=2026&month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/monthly — filtered by site
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthly?year=2026&month=6&siteId={{siteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### ─── EXPORT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### GET /reports/export/excel — download daily Excel report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/excel?type=daily&date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/export/excel — download monthly Excel report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/excel?type=monthly&year=2026&month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/export/pdf — download daily PDF report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/pdf?type=daily&date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/export/pdf — download monthly PDF report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/pdf?type=monthly&year=2026&month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### ─── EMPLOYEE ATTENDANCE HISTORY (Employee Bearer token) ───────────────────

### GET /attendance/employee/:id — recent 7 records
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/employee/{{employeeId}}?limit=7
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

###

### GET /attendance/employee/:id — monthly records
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/employee/{{employeeId}}?year=2026&month=7
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

###
### ─── REPORTS (Admin/Recruiter Supabase token) ────────────────────────────────

### GET /reports/daily — daily attendance report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/monthly — monthly summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthly?year=2026&month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /reports/export/excel — download daily Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/excel?type=daily&date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### GET /dashboard/recent-checkins — recent check-ins list
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent-checkins?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### ─── RECRUITER SCOPED EXAMPLES ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /dashboard/stats — recruiter sees only their sites' data
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{recruiterToken}}

###

### GET /reports/daily — recruiter sees only their site records
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?date=2026-07-02
Authorization: Bearer {{recruiterToken}}

###
### ─── ERROR CASES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###

### 401 — no token
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats

###

### 401 — invalid employee token
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/scan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

{
  "site_token": "qr_mum_central_001",
  "latitude": 18.9748,
  "longitude": 72.8241,
  "device_id": "test"
}

###

### 400 — invalid QR token
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/scan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeToken}}

{
  "site_token": "invalid_qr_token_xyz",
  "latitude": 18.9748,
  "longitude": 72.8241,
  "device_id": "test"
}

###
